
# **Exercise 2.2 – ODD Specification**

| Dimension        | Operating Conditions                  | Non-Operating Conditions                 | Runtime ODD Violation Detection                       |
| ---------------- | ------------------------------------- | ---------------------------------------- | ----------------------------------------------------- |
| Weather          | Clear and dry weather                 | Rain, fog, snow, storm                   | Visibility estimation / weather detection from camera |
| Lighting         | Daytime with good visibility          | Night, dusk, dawn, strong glare          | Image brightness and illumination analysis            |
| Camera Condition | Fully functional, unobstructed camera | Dirty, occluded, damaged, blurred camera | Image quality checks (blur/occlusion detection)       |
| Scene Type       | Urban roads with intersections        | Highways, rural roads, off-road, tunnels | Map-based or scene classification                     |
| Vehicle Speed    | 0–50 km/h urban driving               | Above 50 km/h or highway speeds          | Vehicle speed sensor monitoring                       |

