# **Exercise 2.5 – Control Structure**

```
                Human Operator
                      |
        Emergency override / supervision
                      |
                      v
+--------------------------------------+
|         Planning Module              |
+--------------------------------------+
     ^            ^            ^
     |            |            |
Traffic Light  Pedestrian   Vehicle/
 Detector       Detector    Distance Oracle
     ^            ^            ^
     |            |            |
     +------------+------------+
                  |
               Camera
                  |
        Road Environment (CARLA)
                  |
                  v
            Autonomous Vehicle
                  |
               Actuators
     (steering, braking, throttle)
```

**Control Actions:**

* Planning Module → Actuators: steering, braking, acceleration commands
* Human Operator → Vehicle: override / emergency stop

**Feedback:**

* Camera → perception modules
* Perception modules → planning module
* Vehicle state → planning module and operator

